<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HealthCure - Sistem Data Pasien</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logo.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .landing-hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, #1e3a5f 100%);
    }
    
    /* Glowing orbs */
    .glow-orb {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(100px);
      z-index: 1;
      animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    .glow-orb-1 {
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
      top: -150px;
      right: -150px;
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    
    .glow-orb-2 {
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
      bottom: -100px;
      left: -100px;
      animation-delay: 4s;
    }
    
    .glow-orb-3 {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      animation-delay: 2s;
    }
    
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.7; }
    }
    
    .landing-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    
    /* Logo animation */
    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
    }
    
    .logo-container img {
      animation: logoFloat 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes logoFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    
    /* Title animation */
    .landing-content h1 {
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.2s both;
    }
    
    .landing-content > p {
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.4s both;
    }
    
    .landing-buttons {
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.6s both;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    
    /* Button hover effects */
    .btn-landing {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-landing::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
      transition: left 0.5s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-landing:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    .btn-register {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      color: white;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    
    .btn-register:hover {
      background: white;
      color: #1e3a5f;
      border-color: white;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <!-- Animated background elements -->
    <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-1"></div>
    <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-2"></div>
    <div class="glow-orb glow-orb-3"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="landing-content">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="HealthCure Logo" style="width: 70px; height: 70px;">
          <span style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: white;">Health<span style="color: #d4af37;">Cure</span></span>
        </div>
        <h1>Sistem Manajemen <span>Data Pasien</span> Modern</h1>
        <p>
          Solusi digital lengkap untuk mengelola data pasien dan dokter klinik Anda. 
          Akses riwayat medis dengan mudah, kelola jadwal, dan tingkatkan kualitas pelayanan kesehatan.
        </p>
        <div class="landing-buttons">
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-gold btn-lg btn-landing">
            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i>
            Masuk
          </a>
          <a href="/register" class="btn btn-lg btn-landing btn-register">
            <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
            Daftar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
  <script>
    // Redirect if already logged in
    if (app.getToken()) {
      window.location.href = '/dashboard';
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
